      <acqinfo id="aspace_c30a2931983269918aee5eddbf8a5cb4">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>A small amount of the papers were transferred from the Yale Divinity School; the remainder was given by an unknown donor in 1969.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_d9ef0da7ad025c1a0864d216273a178c">
